item.title: 2025 Goals
item.description: Making goals is weird. They are really just an expression of what I want in the moment. There are genuine reasons that serve me as to why these goals would change. For example, I go back and forth on whether I want to read more, or play more games, or watch basketball. They all are hobbies that I want to do at night, but what I want always changes. Regardless, here are my 2025 goals:
